headline: AEVEX Names Brett Hush Senior Vice President of Tactical Systems
summary: TAMPA, Fla., September 10, 2025--AEVEX today announced that Brett Hush has joined the company as Senior Vice President of Tactical Systems. Hush will lead strategy, product development, and growth initiatives across AEVEX’s Tactical Systems portfolio, working closely with engineering, programs, and business development teams to accelerate delivery of operationally relevant capabilities to defense customers.

headline: Q2 Inspection Instruments Earnings: Teledyne (NYSE:TDY) Impresses
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q2. Today, we are looking at inspection instruments stocks, starting with Teledyne (NYSE:TDY).
